    "description": "Let your imagination run wild and 3D paint an <strong>infinitely generated world</strong> or challenge your friends in <strong>guessing</strong> or <strong>strategy</strong> games.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082860/extras/7447a065b1cf30863bb5c1528a6c47d4.poster.avif?t=1659377177\" width=314 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082860/extras/7447a065b1cf30863bb5c1528a6c47d4.webm?t=1659377177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082860/extras/7447a065b1cf30863bb5c1528a6c47d4.mp4?t=1659377177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Alone or with friends, choose from the <strong>three game modes</strong> that Hue Hills offers:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>3D Draw</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roam around an infinitely generated world and shape it the way you like. You can choose from a variety of colors for every line. Use flying mode for a more accurate design. Give your lines colliders or walk right through them! </h2></li><li> <strong>Guess Draw</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge your friends to a draw guessing battle. Each player gets to chose their own word and has 1 minute to show off their drawing skills! The chat is where everyone takes their guess. Be quick! The earlier you answer correctly the more points you get! </h2></li><li> <strong>Paper Soccer</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This strategy game will put your brain to a challenge up against your friends. Take your time and think at every step! Each move could lead you to either victory or loss. </h2></li></ul>",
